        <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-3">Get your free AI Search Visibility Audit</h2>
        <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted max-w-[520px] mx-auto">Tested across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI Overviews. Delivered in five working days. No commitment.</p>
